author: Shuvra
title: Good running shoes at it's price!
content:
Very light shoes that hold up good while running. The sole is foam and the head of the shoe is actually a mesh.
This helps the shoe breath and keep the feet dry. Running on the treadmill is easy but when jogging outdoors, noticed that the grip was not to fine and did not inspire confidence. However the foam sole along with the good quality insole absorb most of the shock.
The colors are exactly as shown and are neither gaudy nor very muted. Just the right amount.
Still have to see how durable the mesh on the head of the shoe is and how well the foam stands up to the rough running terrains but for a cost of INR1700, I am not complaining about these stylish pair of shoes.

author: Madhavan R
title: Nice but your choice
content:
Pros:
1. Impressingly light weight
2. Nice color
3. Mesh in the front makes good air circulation.
4. Perfect fit

Cons
1. Sole... You may not believe that they're giving such a poor sole.
2. I doubt the product genuine.

But as far as fit and comfort concerned i chose not to return the product.

It was very comfortable for my jump rope workout. But for running you may feel some lack of grip to the ground.
